OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fmostly dry and breezy evening with
OL,7,Flate sunny spells. Remaining dry
OL,8,Fovernight with some clear intervals
OL,9,Fand the odd spot of light rain
OL,10,Fpossible.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FCloudy with light rain
OL,13,Finitially. A mix of brighter spells
OL,14,Fand light showers reaches all mid-
OL,15,Fmorning. Showers building during late
OL,16,Fafternoon, perhaps merging to longer
OL,17,Fperiods rain during evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
