OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FBright
OL,6,Fspells and a few showers on Saturday.
OL,7,FDry on Sunday and Monday with some
OL,8,Flong spells of sunshine, but perhaps
OL,9,Fcloudier on Monday. Becoming warmer.
